捵字的汉语字典释义

[①]［tiǎn］
［《集韻》他典切，上銑，透。］
(1)挺出。
(2)拨弄。指开门或开锁。
(3)撑；推。
(4)使纸湿润后轻轻捅破。
(5)掩，趁人不备。参见“捵入”。
(6)方言。付钱。
[②]［chēn］
［《集韻》丑忍切，上準，徹。］
同“抻1”。伸长；拉。

捵字的康熙字典解释

【卯集中】【手字部】　捵； 康熙笔画：12； 页码：页435第22
【集韻】他典切，音腆。手伸物也。　又丑忍切，音疢。義同。　又乃殄切。與撚同。

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［tiǎn］
["Jiyun" he cut, milled, and penetrated. ]
(1) Stand out.
(2) Fiddle. Refers to opening a door or unlocking.
(3) Support; push.
(4) Moisten the paper and pierce it gently.
(5) Cover, take advantage of others' precautions. See "Shooting in".
(6) Dialects. Pay money.
[②] [chēn]
["Jiyun" is ugly, patience, accurate and thorough. ]
Same as "Stretch 1". Stretch; pull.

Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words
[Mao Collection] [Hand Character Department] 　捵; Kangxi Strokes: 12; Page Number: Page 435 22
[Jiyun] He is classic and cut, and the sound is shy. Hand stretched out.　Ugly and forbearingly, sound 疢. The same meaning.　It's cut again. Same with twist.
